name: AccountEdge Company File
summary: Learn about .MYO files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: To create a MYO file, select File → New File, and complete the prompts.
To open a MYO file, select File → Open, navigate to your file, and click Open.

description: Data file created by AccountEdge Pro, a business accounting application; contains accounting information for a company; includes data describing accounts, sales, banking, purchases, time billing, inventory, payroll, and personalized cards.
